                            <comment id="14074924" author="cheolsoo" created="Fri, 25 Jul 2014 22:11:52 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;The uploaded patch calls &lt;tt&gt;dfs.setReplication()&lt;/tt&gt; after &lt;tt&gt;dfs.copyFromLocal()&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14074949" author="rohini" created="Fri, 25 Jul 2014 22:25:38 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Minor comments:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Can you leave the default at 3?&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Also can you create a MapredConfig class and define the config as constant there.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14075182" author="cheolsoo" created="Sat, 26 Jul 2014 02:06:41 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=rohini&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;rohini&quot;&gt;Rohini Palaniswamy&lt;/a&gt;, I created a MRConfiguration class and refactored all the MR properties into constants. My patch got big, so I uploaded it to RB too-&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://reviews.apache.org/r/23960/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://reviews.apache.org/r/23960/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14075553" author="rohini" created="Sun, 27 Jul 2014 06:18:00 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;+1. That is awesome. Thanks for doing it for all the MR settings in the code base.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14075569" author="cheolsoo" created="Sun, 27 Jul 2014 07:37:24 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to trunk. I rebased the patch to trunk.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you Rohini for the review!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
